Symbol.Script_3D:
! Overhead Cabinet
IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then resol 3 endif
pen gs_cont_pen
ADDy b resol gs_resol material camat rotz -90
rotx 90 for I=1 to 2 prism_ 13, -1/2", b-1/2", 0, 79, b-1/2", 1/2", 979, b, 1/2", 3079, b, zzyzx-1/2", 79, b-1/2", zzyzx-1/2", 979, b-1/2", zzyzx, 3079, 1/2", zzyzx, 79, 1/2", zzyzx-1/2", 979, 0, zzyzx-1/2", 3079, 0, 1/2", 79, 1/2", 1/2", 979, 1/2", 0, 3079, 1/2", 0, -1 addz -(a-1/2") next I del 2
gosub 1000
addz -1/2"
prism_ 17, -a+1", b-1/2", 0, 79, b-1/2", 1/4", 79, 1/2", 1/4", 79, 1/2", 1/2", 979, 1/4", 1/2", 3079, 1/4", zzyzx-1/2", 79, 1/2", zzyzx-1/2", 979, 1/2", zzyzx-1/4", 3079, b-1/2", zzyzx-1/4", 79, b-1/2", zzyzx, 79, 1/2", zzyzx, 79, 1/2", zzyzx-1/2", 979, 0, zzyzx-1/2", 3079, 0, 1/2", 79, 1/2", 1/2", 979, 1/2", 0, 3079, b-1/2", 0, -1
20: del 2
addz 1/4" prism_ 5,1/2", 1",1/2",15, b-1",1/2",15, b-1",a-1/2",15, 1",a-1/2",15, 1",1/2",-1 del 1
material dfmat
add b-1/2",1/2"+1/8",0 rotx 90
prism_ 7,-(a-1"-2/8"), 0, 0, 79, 0, zzyzx, 79, 0, zzyzx-1/2", 979, 1/2", zzyzx-1/2", 3079, 1/2", 1/2", 79, 0, 1/2", 979, 0, 0, 3079
del 2
del top
! ----- Knob if bKnob then
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then
add A/2 + knob_pl_x, 0, knob_pl_y ! old default 3"
if gs_knob_type_m > 3 then if gs_knob_p_m = 0 then addz knob_size/2 else addx knob_size/2 endif endif
call "fa_knobtyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_knob_type_m = gs_knob_type_m, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_knob_mat = gs_knob_mat, gs_knob_p_m = gs_knob_p_m, knob_size = knob_size, bifoldDoor = 0
if gs_knob_type_m > 3 then del 1
del 1
unID = 1 hotspot A/2 + knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A/2 + knob_pl_x, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A/2 + knob_pl_x, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot A/2, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A/2 - 1, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot A/2 + knob_pl_x, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 endif
endif ! ----- End of Knob
END
1000: roty 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
5000:
vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1
coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4
base
body -1
return
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Overhead Cabinet.gsm
line_type gs_line_type
unID = 1 hotspot2 a/2, b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 a/2, b, unID : unID = unID + 1
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
call "cabSymbolType" parameters all doorthickness = 0.5"
Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
call "FM_types" parameters all
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 0, 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` endif
if gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 if gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91 VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
values{2} "gs_knob_type_m" KNOB_STYLE_1, `Стиль 1`, KNOB_STYLE_2, `Стиль 2`, KNOB_STYLE_3, `Стиль 3`, KNOB_STYLE_4, `Стиль 4`, KNOB_STYLE_5, `Стиль 5`, KNOB_STYLE_6, `Стиль 6`, KNOB_STYLE_7, `Стиль 7`, KNOB_STYLE_8, `Стиль 8`
values{2} "gs_knob_p_m" 1, `Горизонтальный`, 0, `Вертикальный`
if gs_knob_type_m < 4 then lock "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size" hideparameter "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size" endif
values "knob_size" range [0.045,) xKnobPosMod = 0 if gs_knob_type_m > 3 then xKnobPosMod = knob_size/2 values "knob_pl_x" range [-A/2 + 0.02 + xKnobPosMod, A/2 - 0.02 - xKnobPosMod] values "knob_pl_y" range [0.02, ZZYZX - 0.02] if not(bKnob) then lock "gs_knob_type_m", "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "gs_knob_mat" hideparameter "gs_knob_type_m", "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "gs_knob_mat" endif
! Enable only Symbol Types without door symbol iSymbolStyleEnable = 2**1 + 2**2 + 2**3 + 2**6 call "cabSymbolType" parameters iSymbolStyle = iSymbolStyle, iSymbolStyleEnable = iSymbolStyleEnable
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_knob_type_m KNOB_STYLE_1 = 1 KNOB_STYLE_2 = 2 KNOB_STYLE_3 = 3 KNOB_STYLE_4 = 4 KNOB_STYLE_5 = 5 KNOB_STYLE_6 = 6 KNOB_STYLE_7 = 7 KNOB_STYLE_8 = 8
